title: Negative Burn V2 with Specials
description:
Somebody requested that Negative Burn V1 be seeded in the comments on that upload a couple months ago. I can start the seed for all but a handful of my uploads that I've accidentally removed instead of stopped, but I won't see the request on an older upload. So if anybody ever needs/wants something that isn't downloading, please leave a comment near the top of the first page of my uploads. It's impossible to check the comments on every upload on a regular basis, but I do check the first page or three fairly often.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Issues 1-21 of 'Negative Burn V2'

Desperado Publishing, 2006-2008, 68 pages each

A very partial list of contributors (because I'm approaching upload burnout) includes Patton Oswalt, Phil Hester, Greg Ruth, Eric Powell, James A Owen, Danijel Zezelj, Brian Bolland, Evan Dorkin... 

That's just the first couple issues. It's a classic series and you should check it out if you haven't already.

This torrent also includes...

Negative Burn Winter Special and Negative Burn Summer Special

Image Comics/Desperado Publishing, 2005, 98 and 100 pages
